    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/b7121f908bda1b1a5f6b35295a0273c9.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/b7121f908bda1b1a5f6b35295a0273c9.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/b7121f908bda1b1a5f6b35295a0273c9.mp4?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VARIOUS BATTLE MODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/0859da3c8f8438e1d0c0072b34c4e3df.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/0859da3c8f8438e1d0c0072b34c4e3df.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planetary Strike offers thrilling solo missions, challenging battles against adaptive AI, and a full story campaign with narrative-driven missions. A powerful in-game editor lets you craft, test, and share custom missions with the community—fueling endless replayability. Then take the fight online across five multiplayer gameplay modes: tense 1v1 duels, chaotic 4 and 6-player free-for-alls, and Clan battles in 2v2 and 3v3 wars for galactic dominance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONLINE TURN-BASED COMBAT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/ab730022573ada9d7931c808240bfa64.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/ab730022573ada9d7931c808240bfa64.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master six unique ship types in a fleet of 18 ships while waging war across 3 dynamic circular battlefields.  Command with strategy and precision - destroy the enemy's planet while protecting your own.  Outthink your opponent and unleash devastating assaults to claim ultimate victory among the stars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SINGLE PLAYER CAMPAIGN  </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/9dc7c014309e4095a20f235bd38caa3a.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/9dc7c014309e4095a20f235bd38caa3a.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the races and characters of Planetary Strike in a rich single-player experience. Tackle the story campaign and custom missions—both built for solo play. Level up to unlock new heroes and factions, uncover deeper lore, and forge alliances or rivalries. Your choices matter: every battle leaves a lasting mark on the galaxy’s fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CASUAL AND RANKED MATCHES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/15955e5058bd4d73e0fe015f0569f74c.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/15955e5058bd4d73e0fe015f0569f74c.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle in Casual or Ranked matches where every fight sharpens your command. Two leaderboards track PvP and Clan dominance, while a tier system measures skill levels across both Ranked and Casual play. Rise through the ranks, prove your strength, and lead your clan to galactic glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VISUAL CUSTOMIZATIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/61d0398e812c27133fb154269c22a8b2.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/61d0398e812c27133fb154269c22a8b2.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personalize your fleet as you unlock cosmetic rewards that make your ships stand out. Customize ship types, thrusters, and weapons—plus your planet and alliance. With 8,000+ profile combinations, jump into strategic showdowns averaging 30 minutes—every battle feels uniquely yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GET PROMOTED</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/33d8ecde6e023b5e1ab1c13faa4ba314.poster.avif?t=1767989558\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246510/extras/33d8ecde6e023b5e1ab1c13faa4ba314.webm?t=1767989558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise from Cadet to Cosmic Overlord—master your fleet, outwit rivals, and earn 100+ promotions &amp; medals. Gain the galaxy’s respect as every mode—campaign, custom missions, PvP, and Clan—powers your ascent, pushing you higher with each victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
